    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">431 Stevens Street Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1881-10-31">Oct 31&#8212;p m</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Baxter</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I have seen your fervid and stirring criticism<ptr target="nyp.00433_n1"
                />&#8212;respond with thanks &#38; love&#8212;if convenient mail me three or four
                copies here (see above)&#8212;please mail one to <hi rend="italic">E C
                    Stedman</hi><ptr target="nyp.00433_n2"/> <hi rend="italic">71 West 54th Street
                    New York City</hi>&#8212;one to <hi rend="italic">Dr R. M. Bucke, London,
                    Ontario, Canada</hi>&#8212;and one to <hi rend="italic">John Burroughs,</hi><ptr
                    target="nyp.00433_n3"/>
                <hi rend="italic">Esopus-on-Hudson, New York</hi>&#8212;</p>
            <p>I write in N Y, but <hi
                    rend="italic">the above</hi> is my main address, &#38; I return there
                forthwith&#8212;I keep well as usual&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
